Chile’s Cruz Blanca Salud Registers Peru Health Services Unit

-- B y   E d u a r d o   T h o m s o n
-- 
2011-10-06T19:21:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/chile-s-cruz-blanca-salud-registers-peru-health-services-unit.html
Cruz Blanca Salud SA,  Chile ’s second-
largest health services provider, registered a unit in  Peru  as
part of an international expansion plan, according to a
statement posted on the website of Chile’s securities regulator.  To contact the reporter on this story:
